test_list_of_several_same_number:
assert [] == [[4], [4], [4...[4], [4], ...]
  Right contains 7 more items, first extra item: [4]
  Full diff:
  - [[4], [4], [4], [4], [4], [4], [4]]
  + []
test_list_of_single_number:
assert [] == [[4]]
  Right contains one more item: [4]
  Full diff:
  - [[4]]
  + []
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 8 == 4
 +  where 8 = <built-in function prod>([1, 2, 4])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
